    "plan_cost_usd": 0.09069045,
    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Root Cause:** Classic off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts`, line 7.\n\nThe loop condition reads:\n```typescript\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n```\nThe `- 1` causes the loop to stop before the last index, so the final item is always skipped.\n\n**The Fix** — one character change, remove `- 1`:\n```diff\n- for (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n+ for (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\n**Verification:** Run `npm test` — all 6 tests (4 for `processItems`, 2 for `sum`) should pass after the fix.",
